    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦认为特朗普关税不会对通胀造成重大打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/ecb-s-villeroy-sees-no-big-inflation-hit-from-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦德加洛表示，唐纳德·特朗普第二次担任总统期间可能征收的贸易税不会影响欧洲央行的宽松计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/ecb-s-villeroy-sees-no-big-inflation-hit-from-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:41:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达斯称，除非通胀得到控制，否则印度储备银行的工作尚未完成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/rbi-s-job-unfinished-until-inflation-under-control-das-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯表示，如果通胀率未能持续稳定在 4% 的目标水平附近，印度央行将认为其工作尚未完成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/rbi-s-job-unfinished-until-inflation-under-control-das-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:33:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入英国股市和通胀的困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-11-21/inflation-worry-uk-needs-to-change-the-conversation-to-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[只要人们还在谈论物价上涨，它就仍会是一个令人担忧的问题，但英国人更应该担心的是停滞不前的股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-11-21/inflation-worry-uk-needs-to-change-the-conversation-to-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:06:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使从黎巴嫩前往以色列寻求停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-21/us-envoy-in-israel-in-bid-to-clinch-truce-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫最资深的中东特使之一将于周三从贝鲁特前往特拉维夫，以期促成以色列与真主党之间的停火。彭博新闻社的 Stuart Livingstone-Wallace 与 Joumanna Bercetche 就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-21/us-envoy-in-israel-in-bid-to-clinch-truce-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:02:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车持续疲软，欧洲汽车销售停滞不前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/europe-car-sales-stagnate-as-electric-vehicle-weakness-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲汽车销量持平，福特汽车公司和大众汽车公司等主要制造商纷纷削减成本以应对低迷的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/europe-car-sales-stagnate-as-electric-vehicle-weakness-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国起诉、取消债券发售后阿达尼股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/adani-bonds-tumble-after-founder-charged-by-us-authorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国检察官指控创始人高塔姆·阿达尼参与贿赂阴谋后，阿达尼集团旗下子公司的股票和债券大幅下跌。该集团还取消了 6 亿美元的债券发售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/adani-bonds-tumble-after-founder-charged-by-us-authorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:53:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持加密货币，比特币价格逼近 10 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bitcoin-btc-on-verge-of-95-000-as-crypto-seeks-direct-line-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币接近历史性的 10 万美元大关，受人们对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对加密货币的支持预示着美国将转向友好监管而非打击的乐观情绪推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bitcoin-btc-on-verge-of-95-000-as-crypto-seeks-direct-line-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 00:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库存增加后交易商权衡乌克兰风险 油价持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国原油库存连续第三周增加后，市场关注乌克兰和中东局势的发展，油价因此趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 23:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
